data.description: LOCATION, LOCATION!!! MOTIVATED SELLER!! Beautiful 5 bedroom, 3.5 bath home in Cypress Creek Addition. Home features 2 en-suites, both on the first level, one of which is perfect for a MIL or teenager. The 2nd downstairs en-suite bathroom has been remodeled with a walk-in shower complete with handrails. Large primary bedroom and bathroom features 2 vanities, whirlpool jacuzzi, walk-in shower and over-sized closet. Three additional upstairs bedrooms. Large downstairs living area features a gas fireplace while the upstairs features a 2nd, open living area and a large game room. Spacious kitchen with a walk-in pantry, SS double oven and cooktop. Newer roof. Granite throughout. Home overlooks the community pond with fountain, perfect for morning coffee. Owner is open to a lease/purchase agreement.
